  stimulus_text = 'The research team has concluded that the most effective way to stop the spread of the virus is to minimize contact with infected individuals. The team’s conclusion is based on data from previous studies, which have shown that the virus is easily transmitted through close contact. It’s important for individuals to understand that they can help to stop the spread of the virus by following simple guidelines, such as washing their hands frequently and avoiding close contact with people who are sick.',
