  stimulus_text = 'The playwright, best known for his work in musical theatre, has won numerous awards, including a Tony Award,  for his groundbreaking work in the genre.  He was known for his use of innovative and challenging musical styles and for his  profound  ability to connect with audiences. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
